{"tid":1630443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一定要道歉，死貓都要食","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:50:00.000Z","uid":107297,"like":21,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"60d0a23253dc4157679b07bc861e51237893bf97","tid":1630443,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:31:56.000Z","msg":"就算係卧底，我地都拎唔到證據出黎，結果條數一定入落我地到<br />\n就算係死貓，我地都要食<br />\n我地要道歉，搶返個輿論返黎"},{"pid":"dd2717dafd3a07afcdac144c1d75b724c9ac3dbb","tid":1630443,"uid":62151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:32:26.000Z","msg":"sage"},{"pid":"f1b80aa5351d884e08fc9fa465c3d17b15ccb059","tid":1630443,"uid":128489,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce4a5564c735a3d2f75b12b3ef158b2f076e74e7","tid":1630443,"uid":32731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1630314/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1630314/page/1</a><br />\n日後文宣重點方向"},{"pid":"966cd06bc7a5088712e3330bb36f955e552d5c2d","tid":1630443,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:34:29.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"87487d202ee9d57c2d040730efffc549240621a7","tid":1630443,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1b80aa5351d884e08fc9fa465c3d17b15ccb059","tid":1630443,"uid":128489,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"60d0a23253dc4157679b07bc861e51237893bf97","tid":1630443,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:31:56.000Z","msg":"就算係卧底，我地都拎唔到證據出黎，結果條數一定入落我地到<br />\n就算係死貓，我地都要食<br />\n我地要道歉，搶返個輿論返黎"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:32:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"就算我地唔道歉都一樣係對家做乜都得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非割席"},{"pid":"cfd701136d9d66b84fa52d9063cd69e1686943e2","tid":1630443,"uid":322234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咁多狗換衫/偽裝證據，認乜野呀"},{"pid":"11216b3da3c397c4225fb859adb86120e62abd30","tid":1630443,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:36:51.000Z","msg":"都唔知第幾個支那五毛要手足認頭"},{"pid":"10d6ab75d5e873efafdce434d3cd278b1d77e926","tid":1630443,"uid":650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:01.000Z","msg":"no"},{"pid":"d745a2181fc0a81bf10a822c8e634c0a684a27ee","tid":1630443,"uid":265761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:42:07.000Z","msg":"強烈反對"},{"pid":"a3a260134e3e2d14fcdc6ffe320ae48d2428cdb1","tid":1630443,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci